title: Xbox Has A Serious Security Issue...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a situation where a bunch of modders are using the API allegedly to send a mass amounts of reports and send accounts to being permanently banned. Microsoft should address this and offer a fix. Thanks for watching!
